============================================================

Disease:     Hepatitis B
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    HBV
Transmission:Blood, sexual contact
Symptoms:    Often asymptomatic; jaundice
Treatment:   Antivirals (tenofovir)
Deaths/yr:   0.82M
Vaccine:     Yes (highly effective)
Discovered:  1965

Disease:     COVID-19
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    SARS-CoV-2
Transmission:Respiratory droplets
Symptoms:    Fever, cough, loss of smell
Treatment:   Antivirals, supportive care
Deaths/yr:   5.0M
Vaccine:     Yes (mRNA vaccines)
Discovered:  2019

Disease:     Diabetes Type 2
Type:        Metabolic
Pathogen:    Non-communicable
Transmission:Lifestyle
Symptoms:    Thirst, frequent urination, fatigue
